oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Young girl fishing with her dog beside tree stump
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of a young unidentified girl fishing beside a tree stump, with her small dog at her side. Girl has caught six fish (holding one), fishing pole is leaned against stump. In the background, there is a river and treeline. Girl is wearing a kind of suit material.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: RG 82: Tennessee Department of Conservation Photograph Collection, 1937-1976
